title: The Senesh Senate - An Inside Look
article:
Q: Do you enjoy the Senesh Senate?

A: Yes I do. I get to know the school's events ahead of time and get to plan them.



Q: What has been your favorite project you have done in the Senesh Senate?

A: The booths in the Hanukkah Funikah.



Q: Why did you want to join the Senesh Senate

A: I heard about it in second grade and wanted to be a representative for my grade.



Q: Any other thoughts?

A: I encourage people to run for office and vote for people you think will represent best.
author: Laszlo Rubestein
